pages.title: Arduino and a TFT Touchscreen
pages.content:
A basic script that displays BMP images from an SD card on a TFT Touchscreen. 

Depending on which TFT Touchscreen component you are using, you may need to make some small changes to the MCUFRIEND_kbv library. If this is required, you must use the download version of the Arduino IDE instead of the Arduino Web Editor. There are more detailed instructions in the GitHub repository.
